@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kccqon(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.abs((0.83 + 0.03))
    v1 = v0
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.cos(v2 + 0.61)) - ((v0 + 0.53 * tmp + 0.33) / wp.cos(v2 + 0.20)))
    data[tid] = v0
